Description: Shared configuration for container tools (Podman, Buildah, Skopeo)
 This package provides common configuration files shared between
 container management tools including Podman, Buildah, and Skopeo.
 Includes storage.conf, registries.conf, policy.json, containers.conf,
 and default seccomp profiles.
